metadata.name: ROBOHEAD - LEPUS
metadata.description:
Meet Lepus,
This is my 6th piece of work from the ROBO_HEAD series.
The design for this robohead was inspired by "Ottan Thullal", a recite-and-dance art-form of Kerala.

ROBOHEAD series is a collection of robot head designs that are built from scratch, every single design will be unique.
resolution: 2000 x 2000
